        <content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&#34;PyShooter&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#PyShooter&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;PyShooter&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;PyShooter&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.python.org/&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/badge/language-python-blue.svg?style=flat&#34; alt=&#34;Language&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pygame.org/news.html&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/badge/module-pygame-brightgreen.svg?style=flat&#34; alt=&#34;Module&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PyShooter is a two-dimensional shooter game in which the player runs horizontally and fires at enemies.&lt;/p&gt;
